<p>On success the validator is displaying the div in black and not green. How to get it displayed in green color. It doesn't add has-success class to form-group div on success.</p>  <p>Here is HTML</p>  <pre><code>&lt;form role="form" method="post" class="form-horizontal" id="anyForm"&gt;  &lt;div class="form-group required"&gt;     &lt;label class="col-sm-4 col-xs-12 control-label"&gt;Meeting Days&lt;/label&gt;     &lt;div class="col-sm-6 col-xs-12"&gt;         &lt;div class="row"&gt;             &lt;div class="col-sm-6 col-xs-12"&gt;                 &lt;div class="checkbox"&gt;                     &lt;label&gt;&lt;input type="checkbox" name="days[]" value="1"&gt;Monday&lt;/label&gt;                 &lt;/div&gt;                 &lt;div class="checkbox"&gt;                     &lt;label&gt;&lt;input type="checkbox" name="days[]" value="2"&gt;Tuesday&lt;/label&gt;                 &lt;/div&gt;                 &lt;div class="checkbox"&gt;                     &lt;label&gt;&lt;input type="checkbox" name="days[]" value="3"&gt;Wednesday&lt;/label&gt;                 &lt;/div&gt;                 &lt;div class="checkbox"&gt;                     &lt;label&gt;&lt;input type="checkbox" name="days[]" value="4"&gt;Thursday&lt;/label&gt;                 &lt;/div&gt;             &lt;/div&gt;             &lt;div class="col-sm-6 col-xs-12"&gt;                 &lt;div class="checkbox"&gt;                     &lt;label&gt;&lt;input type="checkbox" name="days[]" value="5"&gt;Friday&lt;/label&gt;                 &lt;/div&gt;                 &lt;div class="checkbox"&gt;                     &lt;label&gt;&lt;input type="checkbox" name="days[]" value="6"&gt;Saturday&lt;/label&gt;                 &lt;/div&gt;                 &lt;div class="checkbox"&gt;                     &lt;label&gt;&lt;input type="checkbox" name="days[]" value="7"&gt;Sunday&lt;/label&gt;                 &lt;/div&gt;             &lt;/div&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;     &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; </code></pre>  <p> Validation </p>  <pre><code> $('#anyForm').formValidation({      framework: 'bootstrap',      icon: {          valid: 'glyphicon glyphicon-ok',          invalid: 'glyphicon glyphicon-remove',          validating: 'glyphicon glyphicon-refresh'      },      fields: {          "days[]" : {              validators: {                  notEmpty: {                      message: 'Required field'                  }              }          }      }  }); </code></pre>  <p><a href="http://jsfiddle.net/VwPaR/391/" rel="nofollow">jsfiddle</a></p>